english.segment1: Let the sea resound let every knee bow down. We will praise You, we will praise You. Let every tongue confess Of Your righteousness. We will praise You
english.segment2: Let the mountains ring with praises to our King. We will worship, we will worship. Let the skies proclaim what Your hands have made. We will worship, You..
english.segment3: Let all nature sing. Let the earth rejoice. We will resonate, resonate Your glory
english.segment4: Let all living things. Praise You with one voice. We will resonate, resonate Your glory
english.segment5: Let the rocks cry out. Let the children shout. We will worship, We Will worship
english.segment6: Let the waters roar. Praise You forevermore. We will worship You
english.segment7: Let Songs of joy, fill the air. Your praises echo everywhere. From oceans deep, to the sky. Let all things praise You Lord most High. Lord most High
